creator: Avacodo Apps
descriptionHtml:
Always on display and Super Amoled wallpaper keep your screen on all time when you lock your screen with information like date, time, battery percentage, notifications of calls and SMS on black background without touching screen always display on screen with less battery consumption. Mostly part of the screen is black except some information part so that screen look awesome when look on screen.
Super Amoled Always on display app have different features for display Amoled clock on lock screen like Emoji Clock, Theme Clock, Calendar View, Digital Clock, Edge Clock, Picture Clock Analog Clock and Write Text.now you can try new features like Samsung Galaxy S7 , Galaxy S7 edge and Galaxy S8 .
When you want to see the date time and battery level and some important note you can simply take out of phone from your pocket and see without touching any button of your mobile. This is best ,delighting and many awesome features in always on display amoled application.
You can set different wallpaper on your mobile with different clocks styles and themes.Always on display is a smartwatch time on your mobile screensaver. Amoled Photo Clock Wallpaper display your photo as screensaver and with other information like date and time.

Features of Always on Display Amoled Super Amoled Wallpaper:
ON/OFF Amoled display option
Display Time on Screensaver screen
Display Date on Amoled Display Screen
Easy to use
Display Battery percentage on Amoled Display Screen
You can easily customize color,size and font of text which will display on Amoled Display Screen
You can show your own text that will show on Amoled Display Screen.
Different a large number of Clock Styles in every type e.g
Emoji Clock Amoled Screen
Theme Clock Amoled display
Calendar View wallpaper
Digital Clock Amoled screen
Edge Clock Display
Picture Clock Wallpaper
Analog Clock Display
How to use:
* Open app Amoled Always on Display and start service.
* for wake up your phone, you will double tap on screen
* for turn off screen just press power button
* The user can on or off service.
